## DBs registered for this user

> Filled by `/setup-wizard`. The wizard will create standard DBs in the user's workspace (Tasks, Habits, Expenses, Incomes, optional CRM) and register their IDs here.

### Operations

| DB | data_source_id | Use |
|----|---------------|-----|
| Tasks | `{{NOTION_DB_TASKS}}` | Tasks across projects/areas |
| Projects | `{{NOTION_DB_PROJECTS}}` | Projects associated to areas |
| Habits | `{{NOTION_DB_HABITS}}` | Daily habit tracking |
| Goals & Objectives | `{{NOTION_DB_GOALS}}` | Annual / quarterly goals |
| Areas | `{{NOTION_DB_AREAS}}` | Life areas |

### Finance (optional)

| DB | data_source_id | Use |
|----|---------------|-----|
| Accounts | `{{NOTION_DB_ACCOUNTS}}` | Bank accounts and cards |
| Expenses | `{{NOTION_DB_EXPENSES}}` | Expenses |
| Incomes | `{{NOTION_DB_INCOMES}}` | Incomes |
| Transfers | `{{NOTION_DB_TRANSFERS}}` | Internal transfers |

### CRM (optional, if user has a sales pipeline)

| DB | data_source_id | Use |
|----|---------------|-----|
| Companies | `{{NOTION_DB_CRM_COMPANIES}}` | CRM master |
| Contacts | `{{NOTION_DB_CRM_CONTACTS}}` | People |
| Notes | `{{NOTION_DB_CRM_NOTES}}` | Meeting notes / interactions |

### Knowledge (optional)

| DB | data_source_id | Use |
|----|---------------|-----|
| Notes | `{{NOTION_DB_NOTES}}` | Notes ground from vault |
| Notebooks | `{{NOTION_DB_NOTEBOOKS}}` | Themed notebooks |
| Books | `{{NOTION_DB_BOOKS}}` | Books read |

